article_title: ELECTION 2016: Yoder, Hollingsworth to square off in November for 9th District seat

article_metadata.author:

og.description: Monroe County Council member Shelli Yoder and political newcomer Trey Hollingsworth will compete for the 9th District Congressional seat in November.
